column2: SELECT s.*, dbo.fDistanceArcMinEq (s.RA+ ((s.pmra/cos (radians (s.Dec) )) /#.) * (s.mjd_f-s.mjd) /#, s.Dec+ (s.pmdec/#.) * (s.mjd_f-s.mjd) /#, s.ra2, s.dec2) *#. as Separation INTO gaia_X_galex_test1 from MyDB.gaia_neigh_galex_mjd as s WHERE dbo.fDistanceArcMinEq (s.RA+ ((s.pmra/cos (radians (s.Dec) )) /#.) * (s.mjd_f-s.mjd) /#, s.Dec+ (s.pmdec/#.) * (s.mjd_f-s.mjd) /#, s.ra2, s.dec2) *#.< =# -- cone search #/arcsec
